{"tid":2028581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西營盤男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-05-22T01:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T01:42:23.000Z","uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"51f8ad4822165ceb07ac38cb1233db2d73992290","tid":2028581,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200522/bkn-20200522051454606-0522_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200522%2Fbkn-20200522051454606-0522_00822_001.html&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=2a2356ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200522/bkn-20200522051454606-0522_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n墮樓男子倒斃簷篷，露出一隻染血的手。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<br />\n今日(22日)凌晨4時許，西區西營盤朝光街6至7號天興大廈，一名男子由高處墮下，昏迷倒臥簷篷，住客乍聞巨響，循聲查看報警求助。警方及消防員接報到場，於後巷位置發現事主一隻染血的手伸出簷篷。消防及救護員爬上簷篷，經檢查後證實事主已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，證實死者為一名95歲姓沈男子，現場未有檢獲遺書，相信事件無可疑，仵工其後到場將遺體運走，死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=2aeef2d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"9d4a17856667b082ec7e06a60fe12191d01fe392","tid":2028581,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:34:00.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811fc0a8fce24e895f4e5f989939bcf8337afe73","tid":2028581,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"95歲仲睇唔開自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ec1444a15de1fc